OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSunny,
OL,6,Fbreezy and warm on Tuesday, though
OL,7,Fcooler on south facing coasts.
OL,8,FCloudier later.. Chance of patchy or
OL,9,Frain or showers on Wednesday. Sunshine
OL,10,Fand showers on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
